Euro Weakens Against Dollar After S&P Cuts Portugal Sovereign Debt Rating

-- B y   N i c h o l a s   R e y n o l d s
-- 
2011-03-24T23:22:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-24/euro-weakens-against-dollar-after-s-p-cuts-portugal-sovereign-debt-rating.html
The euro fell against the dollar
after Standard & Poor’s cut  Portugal ’s sovereign debt rating.  The single currency declined to $1.4156 as of 8:21 a.m. in
 Tokyo  from $1.4177 yesterday in  New York .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
